{"tid":1690054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（又輸出革命）不滿警暴及打擊逃票　紐約千人示威堵路","createTime":"2019-11-03T06:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T08:57:50.000Z","uid":201464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1809333ff026f033402f4331d95dc1dc78307dd4","tid":1690054,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20191102/bkn-20191102190129699-1102_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20191102%2Fbkn-20191102190129699-1102_00972_001.html&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=7c6da257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20191102/bkn-20191102190129699-1102_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n由於不滿警方濫用暴力及當局擬聘用警員打擊逃票，美國紐約市約1000名示威者周五（11月1日）晚示威。他們堵塞道路，以粗言辱罵附近警員，並在地鐵站跳閘、塗鴉巴士及警車。<br />\n<br />\n示威者拿起寫上「不要讓豬碰我們」、「揮拳打警察」、「地鐵不需要警察」、「貧窮不是罪」等橫額。在歷時約2小時的示威，他們包圍一輛屬於大紐約交通運輸管理局（MTA）的巴士，貼上貼紙及塗鴉一些反警字句。有乘客指示威者拍打巴士車身，一名戴白色面具和穿連帽衞衣的青年塗鴉，令人驚慌。<br />\n<br />\n示威導火線是MTA打算增聘500名警員巡邏地鐵站防止逃票，以及兩宗上周五（10月25日）發生的警員涉嫌濫用暴力事件。在其中一宗事件，至少10名警員闖入一列靜止的列車，制服逃票的19歲黑人青年。另一宗則有兩批青年在月台打鬥，一名警員被拍到拳打兩名黑人青年。"},{"pid":"b646f2c1e19df195e7562d17cf1df602f15128ce","tid":1690054,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d1d165bdb92bc6cf433e4257883c3177f983e4","tid":1690054,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"睇字有畫面"},{"pid":"8319dbf70315c4ca31e3ac89c9061f0c4f023066","tid":1690054,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:08:22.000Z","msg":"<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"d4686d55e2b55378e3e992e6139611f3410a7e8f","tid":1690054,"uid":13303,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"藍絲：美國佬開咗槍啦"},{"pid":"3d1cb31cdb47639c7178391aa28e2c5079f206c2","tid":1690054,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4686d55e2b55378e3e992e6139611f3410a7e8f","tid":1690054,"uid":13303,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"藍絲：美國佬開咗槍啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727e09a9ba060d5d40f96848bbffa1fc39520231","tid":1690054,"uid":21275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:12:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d794a3ea095607702b4a4c0877bfef6774350f0","tid":1690054,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"示威者向警察舉中指及叫侮辱性口號, 警察毫無反應或情緒失控<br />\n<br />\nUSA: Angry activists storm Brooklyn subway to protest NYPD abuse<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nlT_wE9cfq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnlT_wE9cfq0&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=8dc54438\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nlT_wE9cfq0</a>"},{"pid":"a62b429273068ef02202c5336cdc99c604b87938","tid":1690054,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhtZgyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhtZgyf.jpg&h=7cd7fd3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，醒下啦！<br />\n香港警察已經被完全洗腦，<br />\n當所有反政府嘅市民唔係人，<br />\n係曱甴，係害蟲，係低等生物。<br />\n唔好再浪費時間同佢地講道理，講人性。<br />\n唔好再冒被捕嘅險去撚狗發洩心中怒氣。<br />\n唔好再期望佢會回復以前嘅專業。<br />\n唔好再理會佢開記者會狡辯自己。<br />\n香港警察已經壽終正寢，已經被解散咗，<br />\n而家只係由中共控制住嘅政治劊子手。</span>"},{"pid":"60124b0fd3b35ce89baff84031840e68b99b00f9","tid":1690054,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"c611829ee1d00466b6087504345dfd690b0ab425","tid":1690054,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:57:50.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"}]}